Sore no: Dokutoku no iro wo shita chiisana ki ni seisoku suru honyuurui. Oitsumerareru to ushiroashi de tachiagaru. Maeashi wo te no you ni tsukai konasu.

Its: A medium-Sized, walking red panda with arms and a tail.  It prefers the forest and its beloved trees.
Sore no: Te to o wo motta chuugata no lesser panda.
Kyodai lesser panda no kodomo no

Its: A large monster with the shape of a red panda.
Sore no: Lesser panda no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A huge, hairless mammal, found grazing in grasslands in groups.  It eats plants which it lifts up with its long trunk.  When angered, it will attack with its long tusks.
Sore no: Savanna ni seisoku suru oogata soushoku honyuurui. Nagai hana wo tsukatte shokubutsu wo taberu. Mure wo tsukuri, osowareta toki wa nagai kiba wo tsukatte hangeki suru.

Its: A large person with the trunk and ears of an elephant.
Sore no: Zou no doutai to mimi wo motta, kyodai na ningen da.

Its: A gigantic monster in elephant form.
Sore no: Zou no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A medium-Sized animal living in grass and woodland.  It has a large snout with four sharp tusks.  It will aggressively defend itself.
Sore no: Kusa ya mori ni seisoku suru chuugata no doubutsu. 4tsu no surudoi kiba wo motsu ookina hana wo motsu. Sekkyokuteki ni mi wo mamoru.

Its: A person with the head of a warthog.
Sore no: Ibo inoshishi no atama wo motsu ningen da.
Kyodai ibo inoshishi no ko no

Its: A huge monster warthog with jagged tusks.
Sore no: Ibo inoshishi no sugata de Giza kiza no kiba wo motsu, kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large ferocious predator found in grasslands.  It lives in groups of females and one male with a large mane.  They hunt together and are capable of felling extremely large prey.
Sore no: Savanna ni seisoku suru oogata nikushoku honyuurui. Osu wa ookina tategami wo mochi, fukusuu no mesu to harem wo tsukuru. Kari no sai wa Harlem de kyouryoku shite mizukara yori ookina emono wo karu.

Its: A person with the head of a lion.
Sore no: Lion no atama wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A gigantic version of the feline predator.  Its giant prides can be found in the wildest, most savage parts of the world.
Sore no: Kyodai na hyakujuu no ou da. Mottomo hokori takaku, kiken na chiiki ni seisoku suru.

Its: A large spotted feline found in grass and woodland.  It is known for great speed in hunting.
Sore no: Mori ya sougen ni seisoku suru oogata nekoka doubutsu. Subayai kari wo suru.

Its: A large, muscular, spotted feline found in tropical jungles.  It is solitary and stalks and ambushes its prey.
Sore no: Jungle ni seisoku suru kinnikushitsu no hanten no aru oogata nekoka doubutsu. Kodoku de, emono wo tsukamae, machibuse suru.

Its: A gigantic feline predator, similar to its cousins in all but size.  It can be found in the savage wilderness.
Sore no: Ookisa igai wa jaguar ni sokkuri na kyodai na kaibutsu da. Yaban na arano ni seisoku suru.

Its: A huge, striped predator.  It is found in almost any climate on a lone hunt for its prey.
Sore no: Shima no oogata hoshokusha da. Arayuru kikou de mirare, mure wo tsukurazu, kari wo suru.

Its: An orange striped person with the head of a tiger.
Sore no: Tora no you na atama wo motsu, kuro ki no shima moyou no karada no ningen da.

Its: The largest of the giant cats.  It can be found hunting alone in the most savage countryside.
A large spotted feline predator.  It is capable of incredible speed when ambushing its prey.
Sore no: Oogata no nekoka doubutsu. Emono wo machibuse shi, tondemo nai sokudo de oikakete kuru.

Its: A spotted person with the head and tail of a cheetah.
Sore no: Cheetah no atama to karada wo motsu, hanten no aru karada wo shita ningen da.

Its: A gigantic spotted cat.  It is possibly the fastest animal on land and is found in the savage wilds.
Sore no: Baka dekai cheetah da. Rikujou seibutsu de mottomo ashi ga hayai.

Its: A small hooved creature found in large groups in the grasslands.  It has short horns and moves by leaps and bounds.
Sore no: Sougen ni seisoku suru, ookina mure wo tsukuru kogata no soushoku doubutsu da. Chiisana kado wo mochi, chokomaka ugokimawaru.

Its: A horned person with the head of a gazelle.
Sore no: Gazelle no atama to kado wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster in the form of a gazelle.
Sore no: Gazelle no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large monkey with blue face and rump.  It lives in large groups and often survives by destroying crops and stealing garbage.  The males are larger, with powerful jaws.
Sore no: Aoi kao to shikori wo motsu oogata no saru. Ookina mure wo tsukuri, hatake wo arashi tari zanpan wo sunadot tari suru meiwakusha. Osu wa chikarazuyoi ago wo motsu.

Its: A blue-Rumped person with the head and tail of a mandrill.
Sore no: Mandrill no atama to o wo motsu, massao na kao wo shita ningen da.

Its: A large monster in the form of a mandrill.
Sore no: Mandrill no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na ningen da.

Its: A large ape which lives in the tropical forests.  It lives in complex social groups of many members.  Though it is quite intelligent, it has been known for ferocious attacks.
Sore no: Nettairin ni seisoku suru oogatarui jin'en. Ooku no member kara naru fukuzatsu na shakai shuudan ni seisoku shite imasu. Hijou ni chiteki na mono desuga, mouretsu na kougeki de shirarete imasu.

Its: A large ape which lives in the tropical forests.  It is quite intelligent and lives in large and complex social groups.
Sore no: Jungle ni seisoku suru oogata no saru da. Totemo kashikoku, fukuzatsu de kyodai na shakaiteki group wo tsukuru.

Its: A huge ape found in the forest.  It lives in small groups eating plants.  The groups are lead by a large dominant male with a silver back.
Sore no: Mori ni seisoku suru oogatarui jin'en. Shokubutsu shoku de, chiisana mure wo tsukuru. Silver pack to yobareru leader ga mure wo shihai shite iru.

Its: A medium-Sized ape found in the trees.  It is known for its loud calls.
Sore no: Jujousei no chuugatarui jin'en. Oogoe de sakebu.

Its: Ability to swing through the trees
A small fruit-Eating ape, found in the trees.
Sore no: Jujousei no kogatarui jin'en. Kajitsu ga shushoku.

Its: A small ape found in the trees of the tropical forest.  It is known for its calls.
Sore no: Jungle ni seisoku suru, jujousei no kogatarui jin'en. Kawatta hoegoe de naku.

Its: A small ape found in the trees eating fruit.
Sore no: Jujousei no kogatarui jin'en. Kajitsu ga shushoku.

Its: A small ape found in pairs, swinging from the trees.
Sore no: Jujousei no kogatarui jin'en. Fuufu de kurasu.
Shiroi boushi no you na moyou

Its: A small ape that swings from the trees, eating fruit.
Sore no: Jujousei no kogatarui jin'en. Kajitsu ga shushoku.
Ami no you na colorful na moyou

Its: A small ape from the tropical forest.  It can be found in the trees eating fruit.
Sore no: Jujousei no kogatarui jin'en. Kajitsu ga shushoku.

Its: A large long-Necked creature with a large hump on its sturdy body.  It has been domesticated to carry passengers and cargo but is nonetheless bad-Tempered and will spit.
Sore no: Ookina kobu to nagai kubi wo motsu oogata honyuurui. Kachiku to shite hito ya nimotsu wo hakoberuga, kishou ga araku, shibashiba tsuba wo haki kakete kuru.

Its: A person with the head and hump of a one-Humped camel.
Sore no: Hitokoburakuda no atama to kobu wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster the shape of a one-Humped camel.
Sore no: Hitokoburakuda no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large, long-Necked creature with two fleshy humps on its back.  It is domesticated to carry passengers and cargo.
Sore no: Futatsu no kobu to nagai kubi wo motta oogata honyuurui. Kachiku to shite hito ya nimotsu wo hakoberu.

Its: A person with the head and humps of a two-Humped camel.
Sore no: Futakoburakuda no atama to kobu wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster the shape of a two-Humped camel.
Sore no: Futakoburakuda no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A huge, predatory reptile found in coastal marshes and river deltas.  It ambushes its prey at the shore and uses its great size to drag the victim under and drown them.
Sore no: Engan no shitchi ya sankaku shuu ni seisoku suru oogata nikushoku hachuurui. Kishi de emono wo machibuse shi, kyotai wo ikashite karada no shita ni hikizurikomi, dekishi saseru.

Its: A person with the head and tail of a saltwater crocodile.
Sore no: Irie wani no atama to o wo motta ningen da.

Its: A huge monster in the shape of a saltwater crocodile.
Sore no: Irie wani no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large bird with a featherless red head found in the sky of tropical deserts, scanning the ground for dead carcasses.
Sore no: Nettai no sabaku ni seisoku suru oogata no tori. Ke no nai akairo no atama wo mochi, funiku wo sunadoru.

Its: A person with the head and wings of a vulture.
Sore no: Hagetaka no atama wo tsubasa wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster in the form of a vulture.
Sore no: Hagetaka no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A huge herbivore with thick plated skin and powerful build.  It is known for the thick horns on the end of its nose.
Sore no: Buatsui kawa wo motsu oogata soushoku honyuurui. Hana no ue ni futoi kado ga aru.

Its: A person with the head and horns of a rhinoceros.
Sore no: Sai no atama to kado wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster the shape of a rhinoceros.
Sore no: Sai no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A huge leaf-Eating mammal.  It has an extremely long neck.  Its skin has a distinctive brown and white pattern.
Sore no: Nagai kubi no oogata soushoku honyuurui. Shiro to kasshoku no tokuchouteki na haishoku no moyou no karada wo shite iru.

Its: A person with the head and neck of a giraffe.
Sore no: Kirin no atama to kubi wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster the shape of a giraffe.
Sore no: Kirin no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A small mammal known to defend itself ferociously in combat, often fighting off multiple animals many times its size.
Sore no: Hijou ni neimou na kogata honyuurui. Jibun no nan bai mo no ookisa no teki to tatakau.

Its: A humanoid with the head and stripes of a honey badger.
Sore no: Raa tel no atama wo motsu shima moyou no ningen da.
Kyodai Raa tel no kodomo no

Its: A huge monster the shape of a honey badger.  It is ferocious in combat.
Sore no: Raa tel no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da. Hijou ni neimou.

Its: A medium-Sized reptile with a large shell.  It can retreat into its shell to escape predators.
Sore no: Ookina koura wo motsu, chuugata ryouseirui. Osowareta toki wa teashi wo koura no naka ni hikkomete mi wo mamoru.

Its: A huge monster with an enormous shell.
Sore no: Baka dekai koura wo motsu kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A small mammal with a leathery hide.  It can roll into a ball to escape predators.
Sore no: Katai kawa wo motta kogata doubutsu. Ball no you ni marumatte teki kara mi wo mamoru.
Uroko no you na yoroi no hada

Its: A person with the hide and head of an armadillo.
Sore no: Armadillo no atama to hifu wo motta ningen da.

Its: A large monster the shape of an armadillo.  It has thick armor for skin.
Sore no: Armadillo no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da. Yoroi no you na hada wo motsu.

Its: A large hooved animal with curved horns and a thick brown coat.  It is known for its strong odor.
Sore no: Magatta kado to atsui chairo no kegawa wo motsu oogata honyuurui. Nioi ga tsuyoi.

Its: A horned person with the head of a muskox.
Sore no: Jakou ushi no atama to kado wo motsu ningen da.
Kyodai jakou ushi no ko no

Its: A huge monster in the form of a muskox.
Sore no: Jakou ushi no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large hooved animal found roaming wild in temperate forests.  The males have long antlers.
Sore no: Ontai no mori ni seisoku suru, oogata honyuurui. Osu wa ookina edazuno wo motsu.

Its: A person with the head of an elk.
Sore no: Kijirijika no atama wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A huge monster in the form of an elk.
Sore no: Kijirijika no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A huge predatory mammal covered in white hair.  It hunts the shores along tundra and glaciers.
Sore no: Shiroi ke de oowareta oogata nikushoku honyuurui. Kyokkan no umibe de kari wo suru.

Its: A large person with the head of a polar bear.
Sore no: Shirokuma no atama wo motta ningen da.

Its: A huge monster in the shape of a polar bear.
Sore no: Shirokuma no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A small, muscular, weasel-Like creature.  It is known for its ferocity.
Sore no: Chiisakute kinnikushitsu no, itachi no you na ikimono. Hijou ni kyoubou.

Its: A person with the head and tail of a wolverine.
Sore no: Kuzuri no atama to o wo motsu ningen da.

Its: A large, terrifying monster the shape of a wolverine.
Sore no: Kuzuri no you na sugata wo shita osoroshii kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A tiny furry rodent dwelling in the hollow cracks of rocks.  They can be found high in the mountains.
Sore no: Iwa no kubonda wareme ni sumu, fusafusa no kogata gesshi doubutsu. Takayama chitai ni seisoku.

Its: A hairy person with the head and tail of a chinchilla.
Sore no: Chinchilla no atama to o wo motsu, fusafusa no ningen da.

Its: A large monster in the shape of a chinchilla.
Sore no: Chinchilla no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large quadruped with a mane circling its manlike face and hands at the end of its forelimbs.  It lives underground and is fond of raiding the supplies of cavern outposts.
Sore no: Ookina tategami wo motta, yotsunbai no enjin da. Chika ni sunde ite, doukutsu no zenshou kichi no busshi wo shuugeki suru.

Its: A small underground monster that crawls across the cavern wall with its four clawed hands.  It has a single large eye which can shine with its own light, otherwise its stony skin blends in with the rock.  It has no mouth and is said to feed on evil alone.
Sore no: 4pon no kagizume de doukutsu no kabe wo hau chiisana chika no kaibutsu. Jishin de hikari wo hanatsu, ookina hitotsume wo motsu. Me wo tsubureba ishi no you na hada de iwa ni magireru. Sore wa kuchi ga naku, hitori de aku wo taberu to iwareru.

Its: A huge cave monster with hundreds of feet moving along the bottom of its long body.  In place of a head, it has an enormous toothy maw.
Sore no: Suuhyaku fiito mo no nagai karada de doukutsu wo haimawaru kaibutsu da. Atama no kawari ni ha no haeta kyodai na ibukuro wo motsu.

Its: A large cavern-Dwelling humanoid monster.  It has a gaping mouth with many sharp teeth.  It has no eyes and only two digits on each hand and foot.
Sore no: Doukutsu ni sumu ookina hitogata no kaibutsu. Kuchi ga ookiku, surudoi ha wo motsu. Me ga naku, sorezore no teashi ni nipon zutsu shika yubi ga nai.

Its: A tiny amphibian with a long prehensile tail.  It lives in underground swamps and tower-Cap forests on which it feeds.
Sore no: Nagai shippo wo motsu kogata ryouseirui. Shippo de kabe ni tsukawaru koto ga deki, tower kyappu no mawari de esa wo tsukamaeru.

Its: A small rock-Eating creature that lives in molten rock.  It scurries on little feet and swims through liquid rock with sharp wings.  It uses magma to digest rock and spits out burning globs.
Sore no: Magma no naka ni sumu, iwa kui no kaibutsu. Chiisana ashi de haimawari, magma wo surudoi hire de oyogimawaru. Iwa wo shouka shite, atsui tsuba wo tobashite kougeki suru.

Its: A tiny underground monster with large claws and horns.  It walks on two legs and is dangerous when encountered in large numbers.
Sore no: Ookina tsume to kado wo motsu chiisana chika kaibutsu da. Ryouashi de aruku no de, takusan deauto kiken.

Its: A fearsome, long-Toothed mouth the size of a man'S head, flying on bat wings.  It is found in deep caves.
Sore no: Hito no atama hodo no nagai ha wo motta ookina kuchi ni, koumori no hane ga haete iru. Doukutsu shinbu wo tobimawaru.

Its: A large ball of skin found moving around the debris near underground ponds.  It is there that it absorbs dead matter for food.
Sore no: Haizurimawaru hada no aru ookina nikukai. Chiteiko no mawari no shigai wo taberu.

Its: A large creature found grazing on mushrooms deep underground.  It walks on two legs and has the head of a bird with the antlers of a great elk.
Sore no: Chitei no kinoko no mawari ni seisoku suru oogata seibutsu. Shika no you na ookina edazuno wo mochi, nipon no ashi de arukimawaru.

Its: A snake-Like creature living deep underground.  Its head is covered in armor so that is resembles the head of a dragon.
Sore no: Chika fukaku ni sumu hebi no you na ikimono. Sono atama wa yoroi de oowarete ori, dragon no atama ni nite iru
Joukika shita kabuto hebi no dokueki

Its: A medium-Sized monster walking on two clawed legs.  It has two mouths on the ends of a pair of tentacles.  It uses its mouths to digest its victims with acid and rows of razor-Like teeth.
Sore no: 2pon no tsume de aruku chuugata no kaibutsu. 1 tai no shokushu no hashi ni 2tsu no kuchi ga ari, kuchi wo tsukatte giseisha wo san to kamisori no you na ha no retsu de shouka suru.

Its: A huge monster with an enormous tail, covered with thick fur.  They run on four legs and can be found deep under the earth.
Sore no: Futoi kegawa de oowareta kyodai na o wo motsu, oogata no monster. 4pon no ashi de hashiri, chitei fukaku ni sumu.

Its: A tiny underground creature made of a mass of appendages resembling human fingers.  It creeps across the ground like a starfish and eats with a mouth on the bottom of its body.
Sore no: Ningen no yubi ni nita fuzokushi no katamari de dekita chiisana chika seibutsu. Hitode no you ni jimen wo haimawari, karada no soko ni kuchi wo motte taberu.

Its: A large, long-Bodied grazer with a thick mane that feeds on the tops of towercap mushrooms deep under the earth.
Sore no: Chikyuu no okufukaku ni aru tower kyappu no kinoko no teppen wo taberu, tategami ga atsui, ookikute karada no nagai soushoku doubutsu.

Its: A gigantic version of its tiny cousin, this long, slimy creature tunnels through the rocks deep underground.
Sore no: Chika no iwa wo horisusumu kyodai na mimizu da.

Its: A man-Shaped abomination made entirely of blood.  These cursed creatures are only found very near the underworld.
Sore no: Kanzen ni chi de dekita ningen no katachi wo shita bakemono. Korera no norowareta ikimono wa, meikai no sugu chikaku de shika mitsukarimasen.

Its: A creature that crawls along the cavern ceiling with four long arms.  Its body is shaped as the head of a man with a mouth full of shark teeth.  It waits for its prey to pass below.
Sore no: 4pon no nagai ude de doukutsu no tenjou ni sotte hau, ikimono. Sono karada wa same no ha de ippai no kuchi wo motsu otoko no atama no katachi wo shite iru. Emono ga shita wo tsuuka suru no wo machibuseru.

Its: A hideous monster that has the body of a giant mole-Rat and the torso of a mole-Rat man.   It is found deep underground.
Sore no: Hadakadebanezumi no atama to karada wo motta ningen da. Chika fukaku ni seisoku suru.

Its: A huge monster that lurks in caverns deep under the earth.  It uses its wide beak to reach down and pluck up unsuspecting intruders.
Sore no: Chika fukaku no doukutsu ni hisomu kyodai na monster. Hiroi kuchibashi wo tsukatte, muboubi na shinnyuusha ni te wo nobashite hoshoku suru.

Its: A small creature that lives in watery ditches deep underground.  It has a sharp beak and four tentacles with claws at the end.
Sore no: Chika fukaku no kawa ni sumu chiisana ikimono. Surudoi kuchibashi to 4pon no tsume no tsuita shokushu wo motsu.

Its: A huge emaciated-Looking bear with great drooping ears and many sharp teeth.  It is found deep underground.
Sore no: Ookina taresagatta mimi to ooku no surudoi ha wo motsu kyodai na yaseotoroeta you ni mieru kuma. Chika fukaku ni seisoku suru.

Its: A gigantic monster, once a dragon, now adapted to and polluted by the underground.  Its wings fall limp at its side.  Its face is full of incredibly long teeth.  Its eyes are large to penetrate the darkness.
Sore no: Chika ni tekiou shite daraku shita dragon da. Hane wa yowayowashiku yokotawari., Kao wa shinjirarenai hodo nagai kiba wo takusan motsu. Me wa ookikute kurayami wo mitoosu.

Its: A humanoid monster found lurking far underground.  It feigns death, usually near water, until a victim passes by.  It then uses its long arms to drag its prey into the water to drown or strangle them.
Sore no: Chika fukaku ni seisoku suru hitogata seibutsu. Mizu no soba de gishi wo okonai, nagai ude wo tsukatte emono wo suichuu ni hikizurikomi, dekishi sase tari shimekoroshi tari suru.

Its: A small, round humanoid found wandering the caves deep underground.  Most of its body is taken up by a huge tusked mouth.
Sore no: Karada no daibubun ga kiba no haeta ookina kuchi no, marukkokute chiisana hitogata seibutsu da.

Its: A floating pod with eye-Stalks.  It can spray poison and it gives off poison gas when punctured.
Sore no: Me no gara ga aru sora tobu tsubo da. Doku wo fukikake, wareruto doku wo mawari ni makichirasu.

Its: A small humanoid resembling a walking mushroom with arms and legs.  It lives far underground near water and soil.
Sore no: Ude to ashi no aru, kinoko ni nita hitogata seibutsu. Chika fukaku no mizube ni seisoku suru.
Toketa kabuto take otoko no soshiki
Joukika shita kabuto take otoko no soshiki

Its: A strange shapeless life form with an orange leathery skin containing a liquid interior.  It can secrete its internal fluid.
Sore no: Orange iro no kawabukuro no you na hifu wo motsu, kimyou na futeikei no seibutsu. Taieki ga juuman shite ori, sore wo bunpitsu suru.

Its: A strange crystalline creature the shape of a man.  It is found deep underground.
Sore no: Murasaki suishou no karada wo motsu hitogata seibutsu. Chika fukaku ni seisoku suru.

Its: A medium-Sized underwater mollusk with eight arms.  It is the most clever of its kind.
Sore no: 8pon no ude wo motsu chuugata no suichuu nantai doubutsu. Sore wa sono shu no naka de mottomo kashikoi.

Its: A dangerous water monster known for attacking ships at sea.
Sore no: Fune wo osou kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A tiny shelled ocean creature with many long legs.  It has two large pincers on its front limbs.
Sore no: Nagai ashi ga takusan aru chiisana kaisei koukakurui. Zenshi ni 2tsu no ookina hasami ga aru.

Its: A person with the head and pincers of a crab.
Sore no: Kani no atama to hasami wo motta ningen da.

Its: A large monster in the shape of a crab.
Sore no: Kani no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A large predatory amphibious mammal.  It is difficult to evade once in the water.
Sore no: Oogata no nikushoku honyuurui. Suichuu de osowaretara, nigeru koto wa muzukashii.

Its: A legless person with the head and back flippers of a leopard seal.
Sore no: Hyou azarashi no atama to obire wo motsu, ashi no nai ningen da.
Kyodai hyou azarashi no kodomo no

Its: A giant monster in the form of a leopard seal.
Sore no: Hyou azarashi no you na sugata wo shita kyodai na kaibutsu da.

Its: A person with a cuttlefish in place of a head.
Sore no: Ika no atama wo motta ningen da.

Its: A huge sea monster in the shape of a cuttlefish.
Sore no: Ika you na sugata wo shita kyodai na umi no kaibutsu da.

Its: A huge ocean mammal.  It is a vicious predator and can hunt in groups.
